cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image-to-image translation using a generative adversarial network (GAN) based model. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper involves generating diverse images, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
